gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 117, Heat 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Heat 117-109 and snapped a 4-game win streak for Miami. Collin Sexton led seven Utah players in double-figures with 22 points and five assists, as Keyonte George (21 points, six rebounds, five 3PT FG) and Kelly Olynyk (19 points, 10 assists, six rebounds) totaled 40 points in the win. Bam Adebayo led Miami with 28 points, 16 rebounds, three assists, three steals, and three blocks while Tyler Herro added 25 points, six rebounds, and six assists. The Jazz improve to 14-19 as the Heat move to 19-13.
